k" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tam-Xuy%C3%AAn-quan-thu%E1%BB%B7-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-dYBU0BMWy96tMiL8Yl7EFA">Tam Xuyên quan thuỷ trướng nhị thập vận - 三川觀水漲二十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%ADch-du-T%C3%ADch-ng%C3%A3-du-T%E1%BB%91ng-trung/poem-Myfnb3a5aTJoXFc6kLSZkQ">Tích du (Tích ngã du Tống trung) - 遣懷（昔我遊宋中）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%81/T%E1%BB%8Bch-th%E1%BB%A9-Chi-Ngh%C4%A9a-d%E1%BB%8Bch-v%C3%A3n-L%E1%BA%A1ng-S%C6%A1n-hi%E1%BB%87p-tr%E1%BA%A5n-T%C3%B4-Xuy%C3%AAn-h%E1%BA%A7u/poem-_W0oNSCYrVyuJaeugHf8bA">Tịch thứ Chi Nghĩa dịch, vãn Lạng Sơn hiệp trấn Tô Xuyên hầu - 夕佽芝義驛挽諒山協鎮蘇川侯</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%81/author-YFWZ8afu7g2IoLevX1_E2Q">Nguyễn Đề</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Minh-T%C3%B4ng/V%C3%A3n-Ph%C3%A1p-Loa-t%C3%B4n-gi%E1%BA%A3-Thanh-Mai-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-4hxwNBM2h4AsuA1hvhLkJA">Vãn Pháp Loa tôn giả Thanh Mai tự - 挽法螺尊者題青梅寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Minh-T%C3%B4ng/author-4trx3YJ-cefKhX0g_XM7Sw">Trần Minh Tông</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
